org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph

Class ManagementEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph.ManagementAttachment
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph.ManagementEdge

  • public final class ManagementEdge
extends ManagementAttachment
    This class implements a directed edge of a ManagementGraph. The edge is derived from a channel of the actual execution graph.

    This class is not thread-safe.
